@startuml
participant "Payment Service" as PaymentService
participant "Payment DB" as DB
participant "Kafka (Event Bus)" as Kafka
participant "Consumer Service" as ConsumerService

== Pha 4: Transactional Outbox đồng bộ trạng thái VIP ==

note over PaymentService: Outbox Relay Cron quét bảng Outbox định kỳ
activate PaymentService

PaymentService -> DB: Quét các sự kiện PENDING trong Outbox
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: Trả về SubscriptionPurchasedEvent
deactivate DB

PaymentService -> Kafka: Publish "SubscriptionPurchased"\nlên topic
activate Kafka
Kafka --> PaymentService: Xác nhận lưu trữ sự kiện
deactivate Kafka

PaymentService -> DB: UPDATE Outbox\n(status='DONE')
activate DB
DB --> PaymentService: OK
deactivate DB
deactivate PaymentService

activate ConsumerService
Kafka -> ConsumerService: Consume "SubscriptionPurchased"\ntừ topic
ConsumerService -> ConsumerService: Xử lý event theo ngữ cảnh service\n(ví dụ: cập nhật UserSubscription)
deactivate ConsumerService
@enduml
